        <article>
            <h2>Burger king</h2>
            <img src="images/burger king.jpg" alt="Article Image" height="300" width="350">
            <p>Burger King is a well-known fast food restaurant chain that was founded in 1954 in Miami, Florida, USA. 
            It has since grown into a global brand with thousands of locations worldwide. Known for its flame-grilled
             burgers, Burger King offers a wide range of menu items, including sandwiches, fries, salads, desserts, and beverages.</p>
        </article>

        <section>
            <h2>Facts:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Whopper: The Whopper is Burger King's signature burger, first introduced in 1957. It consists of a flame-grilled
                     beef patty, sesame seed bun, lettuce, tomato, mayonnaise, ketchup, pickles, and onions.</li>
                <li>"Have It Your Way": Burger King's iconic slogan, "Have It Your Way," was introduced in 1974. It emphasizes 
                    the customizable nature of their menu, allowing customers to personalize their orders.</li>
                <li>Global Presence: Burger King has a strong international presence, with thousands of restaurants in over 100 
                    countries. The company has expanded into various markets worldwide, including Europe, Asia, the Middle East, 
                    and Africa.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
